title: Alonso returns to F1! Plus exclusive Magnussen interview
description: ESPN's Alexis Nunes and Laurence Edmondson discuss Fernando Alonso's 2021 return with Renault and whether it will prove to be a winning combination. Meanwhile, Nate Saunders catches up with Haas driver Kevin Magnussen between races in Austria.
